Title: A Stony Reception
Description:
<This chipped stone tablet stands out from its surroundings.

As you go to pick it up, it weighs quite a lot more than you expected.

Soridormi will want to see this.>
ObjectivesText: Bring the Chipped Stone Tablet to Soridormi in the Tyrhold Reservoir.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Return the item to Soridormi in the Tyrhold Reservoir.
